---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

---

<BaseLayout title="About Tonypedia" description="Learn about Tonypedia, your curated knowledge hub.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-6">
      About Tonypedia
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-full space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Tonypedia is a curated knowledge hub designed to help you understand the world
        better. In an age of information overload, we believe that deep, nuanced
        understanding matters more than ever.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-white mt-8 mb-4">
        Our Mission
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        We're committed to making complex topics accessible, insightful, and engaging.
        Whether you're interested in the latest technological breakthroughs, geopolitical
        shifts, cultural trends, or the intersection of all three, Tonypedia provides
        thoughtful analysis and curated content.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-white mt-8 mb-4">
        What We Cover
      </h2>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-blue-500 mt-1">⚡</span>
          <span><strong>Tech & Business:</strong> AI, startups, market trends, and digital transformation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">🌍</span>
          <span><strong>Geopolitics:</strong> International relations, emerging economies, and global conflicts</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-violet-500 mt-1">🏛️</span>
          <span><strong>Society:</strong> Culture, politics, philosophy, and social movements</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">🎵</span>
          <span><strong>Music:</strong> Artists, genres, industry trends, and cultural impact</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-500 mt-1">🎬</span>
          <span><strong>Movies:</strong> Films, directors, storytelling, and cinema as art</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-pink-500 mt-1">📅</span>
          <span><strong>Events:</strong> Major happenings, conferences, and cultural moments</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-white mt-8 mb-4">
        How We Work
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Each article on Tonypedia is carefully researched and written to provide depth
        without complexity. We believe in explaining ideas clearly, backing claims with
        evidence, and presenting multiple perspectives where relevant.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Our AI assistant can help you navigate the knowledge base and find the information
        you're looking for quickly. Use it to ask questions about our content, and it will
        cite relevant articles and provide sourced answers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-white mt-8 mb-4">
        Built With Modern Tech
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Tonypedia is built with <a href="https://astro.build" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> for
        lightning-fast static generation, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tailwind CSS</a> for beautiful
        design, and deployed on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Pages</a> for
        global performance. Our AI assistant runs on <a href="https://www.anthropic.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Claude</a> and powered by Workers.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 mt-8">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          <strong>Have questions or feedback?</strong> We'd love to hear from you. Reach out
          via the links in the footer or start a conversation with our AI assistant.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
